%Y A394091 For last instead of maximum we have A344618.
%Y A394091 For run-lengths instead of partial alternating sums we have A357137.
%Y A394091 Row-maxima of A391983, reverse A391984, non-singleton case A391981 or A392374.
%Y A394091 For minimum instead of maximum we have A394092, trimmed A392713.
%Y A394091 The version for prime indices is A394093, min A394094.
